de.uni_potsdam.hpi.bpt.bp2014.jcomparser.xml

Class AggregationTest

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.uni_potsdam.hpi.bpt.bp2014.jcomparser.xml.AggregationTest

  • public class AggregationTest
extends java.lang.Object
    These tests assure that the deserialization of an aggregation and its dataClasses works correctly. Therefore, two dataClasses (one of them is a root node) which are connected by an aggregation are generated and deserialized.
